# Auto-HTTPS frontend for the Dealer's Choice server-list widget.
#
# Caddy obtains and renews a Let's Encrypt certificate for $DC_WEB_DOMAIN
# automatically. With only port 443 open it uses the TLS-ALPN-01 challenge, so
# no port 80 is required. The served root holds the registry's servers.json plus
# the widget (mounted as index.html) -- one origin, so the page needs no CORS.
#
# Requirements: DC_WEB_DOMAIN set, and a DNS A record pointing it at this host.
{$DC_WEB_DOMAIN} {
	root * /srv/www
	file_server
}
